com.mlt.desktop.formatter

Class DateFilter

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.mlt.desktop.formatter.TextFieldFilter
      • com.mlt.desktop.formatter.SegmentFilter
        • com.mlt.desktop.formatter.DateFilter

  • public class DateFilter
extends SegmentFilter
    Document and navigation date time filter. Accepts the following sequences of fields:
    • YEAR
    • YEAR-MONTH
    • YEAR-MONTH-DAY
    • HOUR
    • HOUR:MINUTE
    • HOUR:MINUTE:SECOND
    • HOUR:MINUTE:SECOND.TENTH
    • HOUR:MINUTE:SECOND.HUNDREDTH
    • HOUR:MINUTE:SECOND.MILLI
    • HOUR:MINUTE:SECOND.MICRO
    • HOUR:MINUTE:SECOND.NANO
    • YEAR-MONTH-DAY HOUR
    • YEAR-MONTH-DAY HOUR:MINUTE
    • YEAR-MONTH-DAY HOUR:MINUTE:SECOND
    • YEAR-MONTH-DAY HOUR:MINUTE:SECOND.TENTH
    • YEAR-MONTH-DAY HOUR:MINUTE:SECOND.HUNDREDTH
    • YEAR-MONTH-DAY HOUR:MINUTE:SECOND.MILLI
    • YEAR-MONTH-DAY HOUR:MINUTE:SECOND.MICRO
    • YEAR-MONTH-DAY HOUR:MINUTE:SECOND.NANO
    The separators are optional and eligible.
    Author:
    Miquel Sas
